# Spring Boot — reservation-backend

## Project structure

```
SistemaReservas/
└── reservation-backend/
    ├── pom.xml
    ├── mvnw / mvnw.cmd
    ├── .mvn/wrapper/
    ├── src/
    │   ├── main/
    │   │   ├── java/co/dev/laurapedraza/reservation/
    │   │   │   ├── ReservationBackendApplication.java
    │   │   │   ├── config/          # @Configuration, security, OpenAPI
    │   │   │   ├── controller/      # @RestController — HTTP layer only
    │   │   │   ├── dto/             # Java records for request/response
    │   │   │   ├── entity/          # JPA @Entity classes
    │   │   │   ├── exception/       # Custom exceptions + @ControllerAdvice
